videos.description: Jericho Sims grabs an offensive board and then elevates for a putback dunk for Texas.
videos.headline: Sims starts off with sweet putback slam

videos.description: Kerwin Roach II drops a dime to James Banks III for a dunk and then makes a 3-pointer on the next possession for the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Roach makes back-to-back plays for Texas

videos.description: Zoran Talley Jr. finds Lindell Wigginton who finishes with a nice layup for Iowa State.
videos.headline: Talley connects with Wigginton for layup

videos.description: Dylan Osetkowski sinks a big 3-pointer to add to Texas' 16-3 run at the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Osetkowski puts Texas in the lead before half

videos.description: Zoran Talley Jr. moves down the court and bounces it to Cameron Lard who lays it up for Iowa State.
videos.headline: Talley drops dime to Lard quick layup

videos.description: Cameron Lard denies Jacob Young's layup and Zoran Talley Jr. throws down a dunk on the other end for Iowa State.
videos.headline: Lard's big block leads to slam dunk for Cyclones

videos.description: Matt Coleman sinks a long jump shot to extend Texas' lead with less than a minute to go.
videos.headline: Coleman sinks pull-up jumper late for Texas

videos.description: Dylan Osetkowski explains the win over Iowa State was a big win for them but they are taking the Big 12 tournament one game at a time.
videos.headline: Osetkowski says Texas is taking it one game at a time
